id: pmc-nv97
title: Fresh production readiness verification for pm-changelog
description: "Fresh continuation pass requested on 2026-05-23 to prove pm-changelog remains release-ready after public GitHub and npm publication. Scope includes release gates, GitHub metadata, npm registry status, clean temporary pm install behavior, self-generated changelog, strict pm validation, and final commit/push state."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[3]: governance,release,verification
created_at: "2026-05-23T20:19:57.139Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-23T20:23:17.760Z"
deadline: "2026-05-23T00:00:00.000Z"
author: codex
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: "- npm run release:check passes from the repository checkout.\n- Clean temporary folder installs pm-changelog with pm install npm:pm-changelog --project and generates a changelog.\n- GitHub repository and latest release are verified with gh using free repository features only.\n- npm registry exposes the current latest package version and install source.\n- pm validate strict checks pass after this verification item is documented.\n- Any generated changelog or governance changes are committed and pushed."
reviewer: steve
risk: medium
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-release
release: v2026.05.23-1
resolution: "Fresh production readiness verification and same-day patch publication completed for pm-changelog v2026.05.23-1 / npm 2026.5.23-1 with release gates, npm-source clean install smoke, package doctor, GitHub release metadata, npm registry metadata, strict pm validation, public npm publication, and changelog self-generation evidence recorded."
expected_result: "pm-changelog remains production-ready, public, installable via pm install npm:pm-changelog --project, governed by valid pm records, and self-hosting its changelog generation."
actual_result: "npm run release:check passed for package version 2026.5.23-1 with TypeScript check, 16 node:test tests, production npm audit with 0 vulnerabilities, 25-file npm pack dry-run, and changelog:check up to date. npm publish --access public --tag latest completed for pm-changelog@2026.5.23-1 using a temporary npm config. npm view reports version and dist-tags.latest as 2026.5.23-1. Clean temp project /tmp/pm-changelog-published-ZRnnrE ran pm init, installed npm:pm-changelog@2026.5.23-1 with pm install npm:pm-changelog --project, generated CHANGELOG.md containing Verify published same-day npm install, and pm package doctor --json --strict-exit returned ok=true with zero warnings."
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  pmc-ysps,related,"2026-05-23T20:19:57.139Z",null,null
comments[9]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T20:19:57.139Z",codex,Fresh verification started from clean git status on main tracking origin/main.
  "2026-05-23T20:20:56.104Z",codex,"GitHub evidence: gh repo view reports PUBLIC visibility, main default branch, Issues enabled, Projects and Wiki disabled; gh release list marks v2026.05.23 as Latest."
  "2026-05-23T20:20:56.104Z",codex,"npm evidence: npm view pm-changelog reports version and dist-tags.latest as 2026.5.23, versions include 0.1.0 and 2026.5.23, license MIT, and repository git+https://github.com/unbraind/pm-changelog.git."
  "2026-05-23T20:20:56.104Z",codex,"Package doctor evidence: pm package doctor --json --strict-exit in the temp project returned ok=true, one managed active extension, zero warnings, and no activation or load failures."
  "2026-05-23T20:20:56.104Z",codex,"Release gate evidence: npm run release:check passed on 2026-05-23 with tsc --noEmit, npm test, npm audit --omit=dev, npm pack --dry-run, and changelog:check."
  "2026-05-23T20:20:56.104Z",codex,"Temp install evidence: /tmp/pm-changelog-fresh-vSKl4c installed npm:pm-changelog --project, generated CHANGELOG.md with item_count=1, and rg found Verify fresh npm pm install."
  "2026-05-23T20:21:36.116Z",codex,"Release target update: this verification artifact is promoted to same-day patch release v2026.05.23-1 with npm package version 2026.5.23-1 so public npm and GitHub releases match repository HEAD."
  "2026-05-23T20:23:17.748Z",codex,"Final npm publication evidence: npm publish --access public --tag latest completed for pm-changelog@2026.5.23-1, and npm view reports dist-tags.latest=2026.5.23-1."
  "2026-05-23T20:23:17.748Z",codex,"Final published install evidence: clean temp project /tmp/pm-changelog-published-ZRnnrE installed npm:pm-changelog as version 2026.5.23-1, generated CHANGELOG.md with item_count=1, found Verify published same-day npm install, and package doctor returned ok=true with zero warnings."
notes[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T20:19:57.139Z",codex,Earlier release and npm publication records are already closed; this chore captures only the current continuation evidence.
  "2026-05-23T20:20:56.104Z",codex,The attempted command pm package doctor pm-changelog --json failed because the current pm package doctor command accepts no positional target; rerunning pm package doctor --json --strict-exit is the accepted evidence.
  "2026-05-23T20:21:36.116Z",codex,SemVer accepts 2026.5.23-1 as the npm-compatible form of GitHub tag v2026.05.23-1.
learnings[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-23T20:19:57.139Z",codex,Use supported gh release JSON fields for this installed gh version; isLatest is not available here.
  "2026-05-23T20:20:56.104Z",codex,"For current pm CLI package diagnostics, use pm package doctor --json --strict-exit from the project where the package is installed."
