close_reason: "Fresh production readiness verification completed with release gate, clean npm-source pm install smoke, package doctor, GitHub release, npm registry, strict pm validation, changelog regeneration, commit, and push evidence recorded."
body: This item records the current continuation pass separately from earlier closed release work so new verification evidence remains auditable without rewriting prior closure records.
